      "rationale": "Validation activity uses the identical non-cannulated 7.5 mm screw geometry, rod diameter, and ASTM F1717 test configuration as the COU. The COU is the bench test prediction itself, making the validation activity directly co-incident with the COU. Relevance gap is minimal; the sole acknowledged gap (single test condition) is addressed under the Test conditions factor."
    }
